node.text: Kristen Hanby asks Grandma a series of personal questions while chilling on the sofa. The twist is, Kristen is playing mega-distractor and makes it hard from Grandma to focus! Full of banter and comedy, see the inner dynamic in the Hanby Household in this week’s episode of Get To Know The Family.

node.text: Kristen Hanby asks Grandma a series of personal questions while chilling on the sofa. The twist is, Kristen is playing mega-distractor and makes it hard from Grandma to focus! Full of banter and comedy, see the inner dynamic in the Hanby Household in this week’s episode of Get To Know The Family.
